<i>- [Blows Landing]</i>

202
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:17,048
Okay.

203
00:14:19,851 --> 00:14:22,820
[Grunting]

204
00:14:25,390 --> 00:14:27,324
Guys, you wanna come here
for a second?

205
00:14:28,493 --> 00:14:31,894
- What is she?
- She's a... um, a...

206
00:14:31,997 --> 00:14:33,897
