00:14:47,446 --> 00:14:49,471
I'd like to keep Spike
as my pet.

213
00:14:50,682 --> 00:14:53,116
Connor, this is Spike
and Illyria.

214
00:14:53,218 --> 00:14:55,652
- Guys, this is Connor.
- Hi.

215
00:14:57,355 --> 00:15:00,415
Um, I like your outfit.

216
00:15:01,460 --> 00:15:04,122
Your body warms.

217
00:15:04,229 --> 00:15:06,129
This one is
lusting after me.

218
00:15:07,232 --> 00:15:09,928
Oh, no. L...

219
00:15:10,035 --> 00:15:14,438
<i>It's... It's just, uh...</i>
<i>It's the outfit.</i>

220
00:15:14,539 --> 00:15:16,530
I guess I've always had
a thing for older women.

221
00:15:16,641 --> 00:15:18,268
- They were supposed to fix that.
